Oww!

24
00:02:11,310 --> 00:02:13,070
A wind slash!

25
00:02:13,310 --> 00:02:15,030
Here they come! Here they come!

26
00:02:15,420 --> 00:02:16,280
Now!

27
00:02:23,330 --> 00:02:24,370
I won't let you escape...

28
00:02:26,220 --> 00:02:27,810
Yahoo!

29
00:02:33,840 --> 00:02:37,550
Okay! Set sail for Lost Island!

30
00:02:46,730 --> 00:02:50,540
"A Solitary Island in the Distant Sea!
The Legendary Lost Island"

31
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:55,530
Contacting all squad captains!

32
00:02:55,530 --> 00:02:57,670
Assemble on the deck of Ship #1!

33
